        Selling in Capalaba 2026
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Capalaba's generous blocks, Capalaba State College, self-contained local amenity, and its position as the major service hub of the eastern residential corridor attract a broad family buyer base. Here is what sellers need to know in 2026.
      </p>
